# Command surface

## envctl capabilities

```text
package inspect/import
contract list/show
recipe list/show/create
target add/list/show/validate
plan create/show
run start/status/events/ops/artifacts/validations/replay/export
approval list/approve/deny
control pause/resume/cancel
rollback plan/execute
```

## nu_plugin capabilities

```text
structured read-only views
approval commands
pause/resume commands
artifact browse/open commands
graph/timeline/scorecard commands
replay verification command
```

