I'm thinking about how to compute checksums. I might want to use sha256sum, but I wonder if I should calculate them all in one go or individually. 

It seems like using individual checksums might provide more clarity or specificity. I'll have to consider the approach and analyze which method would yield the best results. Let's figure this out together!
